{"id":124614,"type":6,"name":"陸小鳳","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/21/83/124614_HG73K.jpg","summary":"陸小鳳武功高強，愛理不平事，因此樹敵甚多，常遭暗算，但他總能化險為夷。陸小鳳風流不羈，到處留情，好不快活，卻不知傷透多少女兒心。陸小鳳的生死之交花滿樓，乃一武藝超凡的瞎子，為人不喜女色。一日，花滿樓突聞少女上官飛燕被追殺，遂出手相救，上官燕為報答花滿樓，主動留下來照顧他，二人發展出微妙的感情…","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>陆小凤</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/16545\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">杜琪峯</a></li><li><span>监制: </span><a href=\"/person/16552\">王天林</a></li><li><span>主题歌演出: </span><a href=\"/person/16494\">鄭少秋</a>《陸小鳳》</li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/16626\">劉松仁</a>、<a href=\"/person/17060\">韓馬利</a>、<a href=\"/person/16514\">黃允財</a>、<a href=\"/person/16928\">黃元申</a>、<a href=\"/person/17180\">莊文清</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>Luk Siu-fung</li><li><span>集数: </span>10</li><li><span>开始: </span>1976-12-06</li><li><span>结束: </span>1976-12-17</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>香港</li><li><span>电视台: </span>TVB</li><li><span>编剧: </span>王森</li><li><span>编导: </span>王天林</li><li><span>助理编导: </span>杜琪峯</li>","eps":[{"id":479327,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/479327","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":479328,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/479328","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":479329,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/479329","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":479330,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/479330","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":479331,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/479331","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":479332,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/479332","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":479333,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/479333","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","aird